The main reason for the assertRecent() I wrote was for testing an audit
log.  By definition, I cannot supply the date-or the entries could be
spoofed or doctored.  As long as it was within a reasonable amount of
time I&#39;d be good.  For example 100ms is more than enough time, but 10ms
might be too optimistic due to where the clock is ticking.



